  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load knowledge files. Read plan.md PR-3 graduation criteria.</step>
    <step order="2">Verify all PR-3 task statuses (020-028) are ✅ in TASK-INDEX.md. If any are still 🔲, STOP and report.</step>
    <step order="3">Run `code-review` skill against the diff `git diff master...HEAD -- src/ tests/ projects/spaarke-daily-update-service/notes/playbooks/`. Address findings (or document deferrals).</step>
    <step order="4">Run `adr-check` skill against the same diff. Address findings.</step>
    <step order="5">Run `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` — confirm green.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/` — confirm green.</step>
    <step order="7">Run publish-size check: `dotnet publish -c Release src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/ -o deploy/api-publish/`. Measure compressed output. Record absolute size + delta vs prior baseline (post-Phase 5 Outcome A baseline ~45.65 MB per CLAUDE.md §10). If &gt;55MB cumulative or &gt;+5MB single-PR delta, escalate.</step>
    <step order="8">Run `dotnet list package --vulnerable --include-transitive` — confirm no new HIGH CVE.</step>
    <step order="9">Run `/conflict-check` skill against R3 PR #451 + `gh pr list --state open` results. Document overlaps in PR body.</step>
    <step order="10">Stage + commit per `push-to-github` skill: commit message `feat(daily-briefing-r4/PR-3): W1 Producer — customData enrichment + stubs + membership-scope` with body listing closed FRs (FR-6 through FR-11) and ACs.</step>
    <step order="11">Push branch.</step>
    <step order="12">Open DRAFT PR via `gh pr create --draft --title "feat(daily-briefing-r4/PR-3): W1 Producer — customData enrichment + stubs + membership-scope" --body "$(cat ...)"`. Body cites FR-6 through FR-11 + closed ACs + publish-size delta + conflict-check result.</step>
    <step order="13">Update `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`: change task 029 status to ✅. Note PR URL.</step>
    <step order="14">Document publish-size delta, CVE state, and any code-review deferrals in `projects/spaarke-daily-update-service-r4/notes/`.</step>
  </steps>

